# Infinity Charging Control - Kconfig

config CHARGING_CONTROL
    bool "Infinity Charging Control (SM8250-AC)"
    depends on POWER_SUPPLY && OF
    default n
    help
      Charging control driver for SM8250-AC (Poco X3 Pro).
      Provides 4 modes via sysfs: bypass, normal, 80% limit, 90% limit.
      Also accessible via IOCTL through /dev/infinity_charging_control.